pageProduct.name: NutraLife High Strength Vitamin C 1200 + D + Zinc 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Nutra-Life High Strength Vit C + Vit D + Zinc combines a high strength 1200mg dose of Vitamin C with Vitamin D & Zinc to support & help enhance immune system function and fight illness.

Size: 60 Tablets

KEY FEATURES

• 1200mg of Vitamin C
• Supports a healthy immune system
• Help enhance immune system to fight ilness

Warnings

If symptoms persist, talk to your healthcare professional. Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet

Ingredients

Each tablet provides:
Sodium ascorbate 600mg
Equiv. Ascorbic acid (Vitamin C) 533mg
Ascorbic acid (Vitamin C) 667mg
Total Vitamin C 1.2g
Colecalciferol (Vitamin D3 330 IU) 8.25microgram
Zinc oxide equiv. Zinc 10mg

Contains: Formulated without: Gluten, wheat, dairy products, egg, soy, artificial colours artificial flavours, artificial sweeteners, preservatives.

Contains: Animal products

Allergen Free From: Artificial Colours| Artificial Flavours| Dairy| Egg| Gluten| Soy| Wheat

Directions

Recommended Adults Only dosage: Take 1 tablet daily or as directed by your healthcare professional.

USAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Recommended Adults Only dosage: Take 1 tablet daily or as directed by your healthcare professional.

SAFETY DIRECTIONS

Keep out of reach of children.
Do not use if cap ring or seal under cap is broken or missing.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store in a cool dry place below 30°C
